quran[9{c,v,t}:
40,17,aaj ke din har shakhs ko is ke aamaal ka badla diya jaye ga. aaj ( kisi ke haq mein ) be insafi nahi hogi. be shak khuda jald hisaab lainay wala hai
40,18,aur un ko qareeb anay walay din se dra-o jab ke dil gham se bhar kar gulon taq arhay hon ge. ( aur ) zaalmon ka koi dost nah hoga aur nah koi safarishi jis ki baat qubool ki jaye
40,19,woh aankhon ki khayanat ko jaanta hai aur jo ( baatein ) seenon mein posheeda hain ( un ko bhi )
40,20,aur khuda sachaai ke sath hukum farmata hai aur jin ko yeh log pkarte hain woh kuch bhi hukum nahi day satke. be shak khuda suneney wala ( aur ) dekhnay wala hai
40,21,kiya unhon ne zameen mein sair nahi ki taakay dekh letay ke jo log un se pehlay they un ka injaam kaisa howa. woh un se zor aur zameen mein nishanaat ( bananay ) ke lehaaz se kahin barh kar they to khuda ne un ko un ke gunaaho ke sabab pakar liya. aur un ko khuda ( ke azaab ) se koi bhi bachanay wala nah tha
40,22,yeh is liye ke un ke paas paighambar khuli daleelen laatay they to yeh kufar karte they so khuda ne un ko pakar liya. be shak woh sahib qowat ( aur ) sakht azaab dainay wala hai
40,23,aur hum ne moose ko apni nishanain aur Daleel roshan day kar bheja
40,24,( yani ) firaon aur Haman aur qaroon ki taraf to unhon ne kaha ke yeh to jadugar hai jhoota
40,25,gharz jab woh un ke paas hamari taraf se haq le kar puhanche to kehnay lagey ke jo is ke sath ( khuda par ) imaan laaye hain un ke beiton ko qatal kardo aur baityon ko zindah rehne do. aur kafiroon ki tadbeerye be thikaane hoti hain
